# Summary of timelines

* July 1985 Houston Natural Gas merged with InterNorth, a natural gas company, to form Enron.

* Engaged in purchase and sale of natural gas and power, construction and ownership of pipelines, power facilities and energy-related businesses, provisions of telecommunications services, and trading in contracts to buy and sell various commodities worldwide.

* A publicly trade company whose shares were listed on the New York Stock Exchange and were bought and sold throughout the world.

* . . .

