# Enron

* Whistleblowers&lt;sup&gt;1&lt;/sup&gt;

    + Rebecca Smith and John R. Emshwiller, two reporters of the Wall Street Journal

    + Sherron Watkins, an Enron vice-president, wrote an anonymous letter to Ken Lay

